-- Correct-answer position was heavily skewed (91% at index 1, 0% at index 3),
-- and correct options tended to be noticeably longer/more detailed than the
-- three distractors, both of which are exploitable patterns. This migration
-- rewrites every question's options with the correct answer redistributed
-- evenly across all 4 positions and distractor length/detail no longer
-- correlated with correctness.

